name: StaticBucketMap_getTest
description: Unit tests for the get method of StaticBucketMap.

test_cases.name: testGetExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method for an existing key in the map.

test_cases.name: testGetNonExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method for a non-existing key in the map.

test_cases.name: testGetNullKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method for a null key in the map.

test_cases.name: testGetAfterRemove
test_cases.description: Tests the get method after removing a key from the map.

test_cases.name: testGetWithMultipleEntries
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with multiple entries in the map.

test_cases.name: testGetWithCollision
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with keys that hash to the same bucket.

test_cases.name: testGetWithEmptyMap
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with an empty map.

test_cases.name: testGetWithSameKeyDifferentValue
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with the same key but different values in the map.

test_cases.name: testGetWithNullValue
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with a null value in the map.

test_cases.name: testGetWithNullKeyAndNullValue
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with a null key and null value in the map.
